result.name: Tequila on Davis

reviews.text: Great food. Amazing ambience. Fabulous service. Their Lamb Burger is a must try.
I’ve always enjoyed coming here with a group of friends. Relaxed. No frills. Beer. Tequila. Mexican food. Can’t go wrong.
Came on a Saturday night and the bar was half full, would recommend for a drinks and chill. Service is decent and slushie cocktails are good.
Great vibes, great staff. Great price
One of the best Mexican food in HK!
